<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password - FinSolutions</title>
</head>

<body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5;">

    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%"
        style="background-color: #f5f5f5;">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 20px;">

                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%"
                    style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">

                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 40px 40px 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;">
                            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #0d9488;">FinSolutions</h1>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 40px 40px 20px; text-align: center;">
                            <div
                                style="width: 80px; height: 80px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #f0fdfa; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                                <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                    <path
                                        d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12C2 17.52 6.48 22 12 22C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12C22 6.48 17.52 2 12 2ZM13 17H11V15H13V17ZM13 13H11V7H13V13Z"
                                        fill="#0d9488" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0 40px 30px;">
                            <h2
                                style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; text-align: center;">
                                Reset Your Password</h2>
                            <p
                                style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #525252; text-align: center;">
                                We received a request to reset your password for your FinSolutions account. Click the
                                button below to create a new password.
                            </p>
                            <p
                                style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #737373; text-align: center;">
                                This link will expire in 1 hour for security reasons.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0 40px 40px; text-align: center;">
                            <a href="http://localhost:3000/reset-password?token=<%=resetToken%>"
                                style="display: inline-block; padding: 16px 48px; background-color: #0d9488; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 8px; transition: background-color 0.3s;">
                                Reset Password
                            </a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0 40px 40px;">
                            <p
                                style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #737373; text-align: center;">
                                Or copy and paste this link into your browser:
                            </p>
                            <p
                                style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #0d9488; text-align: center; word-break: break-all;">
                                localhost:3000/reset-password?token=<%=resetToken%>
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0 40px;">
                            <div style="border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;"></div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 30px 40px 40px;">
                            <p
                                style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #525252; text-align: center;">
                                <strong>Didn't request this?</strong>
                            </p>
                            <p
                                style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #737373; text-align: center;">
                                If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password
                                will remain unchanged.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="padding: 30px 40px; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;">
                            <p
                                style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #737373; text-align: center;">
                                Â© 2025 FinSolutions. All rights reserved.
                            </p>
                            <p
                                style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #737373; text-align: center;">
                                This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>